com.kuka.mastering.provider

Interface IMasteringAlgorithm

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMasteringAlgorithm, MasteringAlgorithmEmd, MasteringAlgorithmManual, MasteringAlgorithmMmd

    public interface IMasteringAlgorithm
    Interface for position mastering algorithm.
    This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.
